<p>

<li>The system includes the following major components from outside suppliers:
    <ul>
    <li>Xenocara (based on X.Org 7.7 with xserver 1.14.1 + patches,
      freetype 2.4.12, fontconfig 2.10.91, Mesa 7.11.2, xterm 293,
